      	<h2>About Verge</h2>
        <p>Verge is a Portland-based art curation and collaboration service. We believe that art should be lived with. We love bringing great emerging artists into non-traditional spaces, especially tech offices.</p>
        <p>We are always on the lookout for more spaces and artists. Let us curate your professional space with monthly or quarterly rotations of professional works from Oregon-based emerging artists. Contact <a href ="mailto:alanna@vergepdx.com?subject=Verge art in my space">Alanna</a> if you are a Portland area business looking for rotating art exhibits or if you are an artist interested in participating.</p>
        <p>Verge was founded in May 2016. We currently urate the walls of <a href="http://flickerbox.com" target="_blank">Flickerbox Inc.</a>, a digital marketing agency in downtown Portland, Oregon, and <a href="http://www.redfoxpdx.com/" target="_blank">The Red Fox</a>, a great neighborhood bar in North Portland, Oregon. Help us expand our reach by providing us more walls. Spread the art love!</p>
